  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803020/extras/7bb8d4fa105f9466a6df65337e57339d.avif?t=1727070275\" width=600 height=92 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803020/extras/c4014d89f8c2b5c8641a001d04dd4c85.poster.avif?t=1727070275\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803020/extras/c4014d89f8c2b5c8641a001d04dd4c85.webm?t=1727070275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803020/extras/c4014d89f8c2b5c8641a001d04dd4c85.mp4?t=1727070275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Manny Boxing VR is aimed at realistic Boxing games using virtual reality systems.<br>If you want to enjoy Boxing through VR, Manny Boxing VR will be a choice without regret!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features</h2></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Boxing play with Manny Pacquiao<br></li><li> Various boxing training modes<br>  - Mitt training ( with Manny )<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803020/extras/31351c2a8008ccf63ea75de43e81d9e6.poster.avif?t=1727070275\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803020/extras/31351c2a8008ccf63ea75de43e81d9e6.webm?t=1727070275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803020/extras/31351c2a8008ccf63ea75de43e81d9e6.mp4?t=1727070275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>  - Dummy hitting practice<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=